{"tid":2393813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李柱銘獲提名諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2021-02-03T17:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T23:30:04.000Z","uid":320575,"like":6,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"532cfb6d048087b5a6ea2025277522b99f44bb7e","tid":2393813,"uid":320575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"82歲的民主黨創黨主席李柱銘獲提名諾貝爾和平獎。根據英文網媒《Hong Kong Free Press》報道，兩位挪威國會議員包括保守黨成員Mathilde Tybring-Gjedde和Peter Frolich提名李柱銘，希望此舉可以成為香港民主運動、爭取自由人士啟發靈感的泉源。<br />\n<br />\nTybring-Gjedde讚賞李柱銘在過去逾40年為港人爭取民主和自由，Frolich則指，他為民主、普選、政治及公民權利默默付出，指他啟發了所有爭取民主的人士 。<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎委員會每年10月便會公佈和平獎的得主。經常在示威場合舉英國旗、人稱「王婆婆」的王鳳瑤與及《Hong Kong Free Press》也獲提名。去年諾貝爾委員會宣佈，2020年諾貝爾和平獎得主為聯合國轄下的「世界糧食計劃署（World Food Programme，WFP）」，以表揚其致力於消除飢餓所作出的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/HHEDESOXIJDS3IFPEQGRJVUW4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FHHEDESOXIJDS3IFPEQGRJVUW4E%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=38466830\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FHHEDESOXIJDS3IFPEQGRJVUW4E%2F&h=d84305ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/HHEDESOXIJDS3IFPEQGRJVUW4E/</a>"},{"pid":"40eb7e8404ae1be0b9358d08ba9b6f482166857f","tid":2393813,"uid":60434,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:48:53.000Z","msg":"民主黨my..."},{"pid":"47123f216f69f01c01f203a8a2898c1a781d5aae","tid":2393813,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4d2e03737acb99d1a795352d105438d30ce79a","tid":2393813,"uid":70487,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"40eb7e8404ae1be0b9358d08ba9b6f482166857f","tid":2393813,"uid":60434,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":1